data.description: BACK ON MARKET AT NO FAULT TO SELLER. Discover your newer built home in the vibrant city of Menifee, California. This 3-bedroom home with solar includes a bonus room, perfect for a home office, guest suite, or playroom. With 2 well-appointed bathrooms, there's ample space for your family's needs. Throughout the main areas of the home, you'll find low maintenance vinyl flooring that not only looks fantastic but also stands up to the demands of everyday life while the bedrooms offer cushy carpets. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, blending elegance with functionality. The open concept design seamlessly connects it to the living area, creating a perfect space for entertaining and daily family life. The EXPANSIVE backyard is fully landscape and so large, your design options would be endless. Pool, patio, and BBQ area can easily go in with still having enough space to add a playground. The two-car garage provides secure parking and ample storage space for your convenient. The front yard is thoughtfully landscaped with native desert plants offering water efficiency and enhancing the natural beauty of the California desert that Menifee residents cherish. Nestled in a family friendly community and the real gem is the brand new community park, just walking distance from your front door. This park offers endless opportunities for recreation, picnics, and community events, adding to the already Menifee lifestyle. This loan is VA ASSUMABLE WITH AN EXTREMLY LOW INTEREST RATE. Call me for more details.
